{"tid":1794718,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"「聖誕市道」零售寒冬！商戶料聖誕假期生意額繼續慘淡","createTime":"2019-12-23T10:33:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-23T10:36:58.000Z","uid":208505,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"bc9b73d6b8efa65b69c432482518e92848d672f7","tid":1794718,"uid":208505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T10:33:32.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】訪港旅客人數已經連續5個月按年減少，有商店表示近期生意大跌，看淡聖誕旺季銷情。個別商店更要裁員及縮減分店以減輕經營壓力。 <br />\n<br />\n社會事件影響訪港旅客大跌，在聖誕及農曆新年傳統消費旺季，不少商店表示旅客人數明顯減少，入貨策略都轉審慎，亦有商戶表示客人消費力大不如前。<br />\n<br />\n連鎖藥妝店安欣母嬰藥粧生活百貨負責人徐斌表示，近期生意由以往月入300萬元，跌至只有數十萬元。生意大受影響，公司要求員工放無薪假之餘，更裁減部分員工，對旺季銷情未敢樂觀。<br />\n<br />\n公司年初在荃灣開設新店，亦因為生意差，上月已經結業。至於其他地區分店，部分獲得業主減租，可以減輕到租金成本，今個月開始公司亦都變陣，開網店作網上賣貨，開拓新的銷售平台以提升收入。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/finance/player?newsId=374349&amp;refer=Share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Ffinance%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D374349%26refer%3DShare&d=HJ1jiXHXfxJ2%2FxolOfbUwfFBXrQbHxe6tNmRytRnjp4%3D&h=806d016c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Ffinance%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D374349%26refer%3DShare&h=f80fc968\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/finance/player?newsId=374349&amp;refer=Share</a>"},{"pid":"d3d523fa9738640086526e2b89241eaf47d68ecc","tid":1794718,"uid":208505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T10:34:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">繼續攬炒</span></span>"},{"pid":"0ccb6c34b1d480b3a69bbd20d189fdf76398b2ef","tid":1794718,"uid":208505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T10:34:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">繼續攬炒</span></span>"},{"pid":"0cb26b96eac93464590442e8e1b333101a73346e","tid":1794718,"uid":208505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T10:34:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">繼續攬炒</